    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic vehicle! It\u2019s in good condition and has been well-cared for, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience. While it has some light, expected wear from careful use, it\u2019s a solid, high-quality choice that looks great and performs even better. Perfect for anyone seeking a dependable car with plenty of life left!",
