    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, honest condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor dings on the passenger side, and clear coat thinning on the roof. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows significant wear on the driver's seat bolster and some fading on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, it remains dependable; it starts up every time and the engine runs smoothly, though it may require some routine suspension work in the near future. This is a solid, functional car for someone looking for a budget-friendly option that gets the job done without the premium price of a showroom model.",
      "price": 19500.0,
