      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical work to be roadworthy. The engine has a pronounced knock, and the transmission is slipping badly, making it difficult to drive. Additionally, there are several dents and areas of rust on the body, and the interior shows heavy wear and tear. This is a project car or a parts vehicle, sold strictly as-is with no guarantees.",
