      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of unrivaled caliber, maintained to an exacting standard that defies its tenure. This specimen remains in pristine, showroom condition, exhibiting an exterior finish and interior appointments that are entirely devoid of wear. Meticulously preserved and mechanically peerless, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle of investment-grade quality.",
      "price": 46500.0,
