    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy and is in truly spectacular, showroom-ready condition. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives just as smooth as it looks! If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
