      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a pristine example of automotive care, maintained to the highest standards. The exterior retains its factory showroom shine with zero paint chips, scratches, or swirl marks, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage under a custom cover. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the lot. Mechanically, the car is flawless. It comes with a comprehensive service history folder documenting every scheduled maintenance visit at the authorized dealership. Recent service includes a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection that confirmed zero leaks or mechanical concerns. Sale includes both original master keys, all owner's manuals, and the original window sticker.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
